OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with clear spells, though some
OL,7,Fcloud developing later, with lower
OL,8,Fcloud possible to the east.
OL,9,FTemperatures will fall under the cloud
OL,10,Fbreaks to give a patchy rural frost.
OL,11,FMilder by the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,14,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,15,FStaying dry with some sunny spells.
OL,16,FBut the potential for some low cloud
OL,17,Fto linger around coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
